This is the Debian GNU/Linux prepackaged version of OPIE.

The debian package is maintained by Michael Stone <mstone@debian.org> from
source available at http://inner.net/pub/opie/. The debian package was
originally assembled by Matt Kern <Matt.Kern@pobox.com>.

The changes to the source were restricted to the build system to make it
compatible with Debian.

This software is bound by the Inner Net License Version 2 and the US Naval
Research Laboratory License Version 1.1 both of which are reproduced below.

